HEADWORD: Monandry
<hw>Mo*nan"dry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Monandria</er>.]</ety> <def>The possession by a woman of only one
husband at the same time; -- contrasted with
<xex>polyandry</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monanthous</ent>⟦br⟧
